text: Geraldine O'Callaghan is a female kickboxer and World Muaythai Council title holder. O'Callaghan has fought 30 times and lost 10 times. ==References== Category:Living people Category:People from Ramsgate Category:English female kickboxers Category:Female Muay Thai practitioners Category:English expatriate sportspeople in Thailand Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
